,"value":" There are only so many hours in the day, which means that I need to be\ncareful about what I commit to spending time on. I try to figure out what are the most\nimportant things to do, and ensure I make space for this work before other stuff.","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"key":"CnyeVQ64fj"}],"key":"kDmQ09WwM8"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1},"end":{"line":30,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1},"end":{"line":28,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Be (conservatively) realistic.","position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1},"end":{"line":28,"column":1}},"key":"E7VL9th3kD"}],"key":"O71e05UUk0"},{"type":"text","value":" I often get too optimistic with my time and energy levels.\nSometimes you’re tired, sometimes you get distracted, sometimes new work pops up you didn’t\naccount for. For this reason, I only budget about ","position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1},"end":{"line":28,"column":1}},"key":"PxocbIVGMo"},{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1},"end":{"line":28,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"20 hours of diligent work a week","position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1},"end":{"line":28,"column":1}},"key":"apNmtwjGCm"}],"key":"tjfSNvjWUh"},{"type":"text","value":".","position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1},"end":{"line":28,"column":1}},"key":"PWnioDfO1d"}],"key":"bOFhbjG4wL"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":32,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":31,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Be flexible.","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1},"end":{"line":31,"column":1}},"key":"DMc1NykOFt"}],"key":"bkhi1jgQlp"},{"type":"text","value":" Finally, don’t worry about following the plan obsessively. Use it as a guide,\nnot a set of chains. If it’s